<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150307>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A–H. Habitus of Acalypta species from Japan, dorsal and lateral view. A. cooleyi, brachypterous male (A, E) and macropterous female (B, F); A. pallidicoronata sp. nov., brachypterous male (C, G) and female (D, H). Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150313>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A–D. Apical part of abdomen, ventral view. A. cooleyi, male (A) and female (C); A. pallidicoronata sp. nov., male (B) and female (D). Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150313/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

